latestIgtvVideos.title: @arianagrande inspired Makeup Look💄
How to shave your face using razor?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Shaving is handsdown the best method to remove facial hair for me. I've been doing it two years since now and believe me I've never been to the Salon in last two years. People have quite a few myths about shaving so I just wanna talk about the myths today
Myth 1-
*Shaving causes hair to grow back thicker*
When the hair gets shaved, it gets cut down at the shaft and hence while growing back it just appears to be thicker. A razor cannot change the colour, thickness or growth rate of the hair.

Myth 2-
*It makes your skin rough*
Shaving exfoliates your skin by removing dead skin cells along with the hair, leaving your skin feeling soft and smooth.
